title="Indexing of truncation levels">truncation level</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
  <fr:ol><fr:li>When <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n=-2]]></fr:tex>, we recall from <fr:ref
